        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Communist Countries Participating in Lobbying Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits former Members of Congress from lobbying the federal government on behalf of communist countries (or entities that are owned or controlled by such countries) and establishes specific monetary penalties for violations.</p>]]>
        </text>
