      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Lobbying Disclosure Act of 1995 to prohibit a former Member of Congress from making a lobbying contact under such Act on behalf of a client which is a Communist country, and for other purposes.</title>
